description.en:
rivapp Network consists of Priva Token (PRIVA) and all the services provided over privapp.network application without compromising your safety and privacy.
PRIVA is a utility token serving multiple purposes and ensures the safety and growth of our network.
At first sight, PRIVA is a multi-functional token that drives behavior for both end-users & developers.
